<div class="wrapper hidden-xs">
  <%= render "components/navbar.html" %>
  <p class="credit">Photo credit: Alexander Hall/imagebank.sweden.se</p>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="language">
      <%= link_to nodsituationer_path, class: "flag-padding" do %>
        <%= image_tag("https://res.cloudinary.com/ddwuu1y0i/image/upload/v1552305881/swedish-flag.png",:class=>"flag") %>
        <p class="flag-text-white">Svenska</p>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to emergencies_path, class: "flag-padding" do %>
        <%= image_tag("https://res.cloudinary.com/ddwuu1y0i/image/upload/v1552305881/british-flag.png",:class=>"flag") %>
        <p class="flag-text-white flag-active">English</p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="container-yellow">
      <h1>EMERGENCIES</h1>
      <p>We can assist Swedish nationals who find themselves in difficulty while in Glasgow or most of the rest of Scotland.</p>
      <p>If you are seriously ill or injured, are the victim of a crime, or face other difficult personal circumstances then we can provide help and advice.</p>
      <p>For all normal consular matters call: +44 (0)141 204 4041. If appropriate please leave a message.</p>
      <p class="short-line">Strictly in&nbsp<span class="strong-text">emergencies only</span>&nbspcall David Hunter, Consul: +44 (0)7767 432 203.</p>
      <h2 class="emergencies-padding-top">EMERGENCY PASSPORTS</h2>
      <p>The Glasgow consulate can issue emergency passports – see <a href="passports" class="passports-link">PASSPORTS</a> for advice.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

